# HEXGEM

Hexgem is a puzzle game for the OpenPandora (with ports to Switch and now Vita), much like ZooKeeper, but with hexagon.

Use the touch screen. That's all.

# Code and GFX by Pepone

# Music by FoxSynergy (http://opengameart.org/users/foxsynergy)

# Font by spicypixel (http://www.spicypixel.net/2008/01/16/fontpack-royalty-free-bitmap-fonts/)

# Switch port by carstene1ns

# Vita port by caghandemir
